# format:
# <scope>|<forbidden_scope>|<message>
#
# default layered Go service rules:
# Add repository-specific extensions in .orch/rules/<target>/local.arch.rules.
internal/service|internal/transport|service must not depend on transport
internal/transport|internal/infra/store|transport must not depend on concrete stores
internal/transport|internal/infra/objectstore|transport must not depend on object store adapters
internal/transport|internal/infra/provider|transport must not depend on provider adapters
internal/runtime|internal/transport|runtime must not depend on transport
internal/infra|internal/transport|infrastructure must not depend on transport
